UPPLIERS FOR ALL DAMAGES, LOSSES, CLAIMS AND CAUSES OF ACTION ARISING OUT OF OR RELATING TO THESE TERMS OR YOUR USE OF THE QWIKTASK SERVICE, INCLUDING WITHOUT LIMITATION YOUR INTERACTIONS WITH OTHER USERS OF THE QWIKTASK SERVICE (WHETHER IN CONTRACT, TORT INCLUDING NEGLIGENCE, WARRANTY OR OTHERWISE) EXCEED THE AMOUNT PAID BY YOU, IF ANY, TO QWIKTASK DURING THE TWELVE MONTHS IMMEDIATELY PRECEDING THE DAY THE ACT OR OMISSION OCCURRED THAT GAVE RISE TO YOUR CLAIM OR $100, WHICHEVER IS GREATER.</p>\r\n<p style=\\"line-height: 150%;\\">\r\n	<b>Termination and Changes to the QwikTask Service</b></p>\r\n<p style=\\"line-height: 150%;\\">\r\n	We may terminate your account on the QwikTask Service, delete your account and any Content you have Posted on or through the QwikTask Service, and/or prohibit you from using or accessing the QwikTask Service (or any portion thereof) for any or no reason, at any time in our sole discretion, with or without notice. Further, we reserve the right to change any aspect or feature of the QwikTask Service at any time without notice. The following sections will survive any termination of your use of the QwikTask Service: Prohibited Conduct, User Content, Your Privacy Practices, Ownership; Proprietary Rights, Licenses, Submissions, User Disputes; Complaints, Indemnity, General Disclaimers, Limitation on Liability, Termination and Changes to the QwikTask Service, Arbitration, Governing Law; Venue and Jurisdiction and Other.</p>\r\n<p style=\\"line-height: 150%;\\">\r\n	<b>Arbitration</b></p>\r\n<p style=\\"line-height: 150%;\\">\r\n	Except as set forth in the paragraph below, you agree that all claims and disputes between you and QwikTask that arise out of or relate in any way to the Terms or your use of the QwikTask Service will be resolved either by (a) binding arbitration by a single arbitrator in Delaware or (b) binding non-appearance based arbitration conducted by telephone, online or based solely on written submission. Such arbitration will