=\\"\\" serif=\\"\\" style=\\"font-size: 7pt;\\" times=\\"\\">OK&nbsp; </span></b><span new=\\"\\" roman=\\"\\" serif=\\"\\" style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\" times=\\"\\">Upload videos to where you want<br />\r\n					&nbsp;</span><b><span color:=\\"\\" new=\\"\\" roman=\\"\\" serif=\\"\\" style=\\"font-size: 7pt;\\" times=\\"\\">OK&nbsp; </span></b><span new=\\"\\" roman=\\"\\" serif=\\"\\" style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\" times=\\"\\">Digg your website<br />\r\n					&nbsp;</span><b><span color:=\\"\\" new=\\"\\" roman=\\"\\" serif=\\"\\" style=\\"font-size: 7pt;\\" times=\\"\\">OK&nbsp; </span></b><span new=\\"\\" roman=\\"\\" serif=\\"\\" style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\" times=\\"\\">Join a Facebook group<br />\r\n					&nbsp;</span><b><span color:=\\"\\" new=\\"\\" roman=\\"\\" serif=\\"\\" style=\\"font-size: 7pt;\\" times=\\"\\">OK&nbsp; </span></b><span new=\\"\\" roman=\\"\\" serif=\\"\\" style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\" times=\\"\\">Add someone to Facebook, Myspace, etc. friends list<br />\r\n					&nbsp;</span><b><span color:=\\"\\" new=\\"\\" roman=\\"\\" serif=\\"\\" style=\\"font-size: 7pt;\\" times=\\"\\">OK&nbsp; </span></b><span new=\\"\\" roman=\\"\\" serif=\\"\\" style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\" times=\\"\\">Vote for you<br />\r\n					&nbsp;</span><b><span color:=\\"\\" new=\\"\\" roman=\\"\\" serif=\\"\\" style=\\"font-size: 7pt;\\" times=\\"\\">OK&nbsp; </span></b><span new=\\"\\" roman=\\"\\" serif=\\"\\" style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\" times=\\"\\">Sign up with your referral link<br />\r\n					&nbsp;</span><b><span color:=\\"\\" new=\\"\\" roman=\\"\\" serif=\\"\\" style=\\"font-size: 7pt;\\" times=\\"\\">OK</span></b><span new=\\"\\" roman=\\"\\" serif=\\"\\" style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\" times=\\"\\">&nbsp; Tell their opinion<br />\r\n					&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; etc.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n				<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\" style=\\"line-height: normal;\\">\r\n					<span new=\\"\\" roman=\\"\\" serif=\\"\\" style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\" times=\\"\\">We take sp